name: Alphabetical Disorder
description:
A nonsense alphabet that rhymes. Written and illustrated by Lo Cole.

"Lo Cole's dotty little book is a total delight" Glen Baxter

This little book was born as a result of a snapped Achilles tendon, a dog that needed to be walked and a mind that really should have been concentrating on other, more serious matters ...

32 pages, black and white.
15cm square.
Paperback
ISBN: 978-0-9570920-0-6
Imaginary Press, 2012  Lo Cole. All rights reserved.

Books are shipped Royal Mail First Class.
